enb_long_title: United Nations Climate Change Conference - Bali
section_title: REVIEW OF INITIAL REPORTS AND SUPPLEMENTARY INFORMATION UNDER PROTOCOL ARTICLE 7.2:
sentences: This issue (FCCC/SBI/2007/INF.10) was considered by the SBI on 5 December, and in a contact group and informal consultations co-chaired by Anke Herold (Germany) and Nagmeldin Elhassan (Sudan).
Discussions focused, inter alia , on the review of initial reports that Annex I Protocol parties were required to submit in 2007.
The SBI adopted the conclusions on 10 December.
